title: 048 - Gumpy Checks In
description: On today's show, the guys discuss the new Netflix show, "Alone," and get Gumpy on the line to check in from Canada to see how he's dealing with everything and ask when/if they're ever going to see him again. They also dive through some #PodFacts, and see where the conversation goes on a Feel Good Friday. Have a good weekend, enjoy.
